      <abstract displayLabel="Abstract">The objective of NIST SP 800-53 is to provide a set of security
                controls that can satisfy the breadth and depth of security requirements levied on
                information systems and organizations and that is consistent with and complementary
                to other established information security standards. Revision 3 is the first major
                update since December 2005 and includes significant improvements to the security
                control catalog.</abstract>
